*note : webflux not working under 2.0.4 and java 10, as on 10/9/18
so using boot 2.0.3 and java 8 (from spring.io)

select web reactive dependency

router : allows url and map to handler method
handler : generate response

rest client can be used 
type request : get
link : http://localhost:8080/hello
output : Hello, Spring!


source : spring.io guides
